This is too hard.

152
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,096
(Someone is happy)

153
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,752
(Someone is worried)

154
00:04:58,120 --> 00:05:00,840
♪I think I will start to miss you♪

155
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:03,920
♪But I just met you♪

156
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,680
