159
00:05:15,547 --> 00:05:17,056
(Bro, well done)

160
00:05:17,847 --> 00:05:19,584
(Got it)

161
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,400
That's about it.

162
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,800
So hard. These two songs are so similar.

163
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,016
You're freaking out.

164
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,480
Do you know?

165
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,480
I know, but...

166
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,632
(Mute)

167
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,120
It's quite hard to sing.

168
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,448
(He's been there)

169
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,800
Let me try.

170
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,824
(Starting to try)

171
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:41,000
♪I think I will start to miss you♪

172
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,800
♪But I just met you♪

173
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:46,800
♪I suspect this luck is a prank♪

174
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,920
