175
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,280
This is indeed hard.

176
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,520
This is really hard.

177
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,120
Oh my god.

178
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,360
