181
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,440
Seriously.

182
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,600
So similar.

183
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,208
(I get you)

184
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:00,680
Wait, let me

185
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,800
take it off.

186
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,360
I only know the tune of one line.

187
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,360
I forgot the rest.

188
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,440
How does that song go?

189
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,840
Let me try.

190
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,560
♪If I could♪

191
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,840
♪I want to be with you♪

192
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,160
♪Back to the day we met♪

193
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,000
♪Make time stop♪

194
00:06:23,455 --> 00:06:24,832
(It's over)

195
00:06:27,392 --> 00:06:29,216
(Are you sure?)

196
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:31,680
I can't even

197
