198
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,808
♪If I could♪

199
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:39,960
♪I want to be with you♪

200
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,680
♪Back to the day we met♪

201
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,360
♪Make time stop♪

202
