211
00:07:10,344 --> 00:07:10,840
(Pass the song The Flower Guardian)

212
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,360
♪If I could♪

213
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:15,296
♪I want to be with you,
back to the day we met♪

214
00:07:15,296 --> 00:07:16,440
♪Make time stop♪

215
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,640
♪Make time stop♪

216
