237
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,480
♪If I could♪

238
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,160
♪I want to be with you♪

239
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,080
♪Back to the day we met♪

240
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,480
♪Make time stop♪

241
