♪I just want to hold you...♪

243
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,720
("Hu hei")
♪Kiss your breath♪

244
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:26,040
Okay.

245
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,800
