00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,880
No, I guessed a song.

561
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:09,120
(Lack of confidence)
Bit he said it was wrong.

562
00:20:09,312 --> 00:20:10,520
(Was I wrong?)

563
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:12,720
How about you sing it?

564
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:15,080
Sing it to the melody you guessed.

565
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:18,280
Put the headphones on her
and let her sing.

566
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,360
The song you guessed.

567
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,320
♪What I miss is♪

568
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:26,280
♪The unreserved conversations♪

569
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:28,768
(Recovering the correct melody)
♪What I miss is dreaming together♪

570
00:20:29,024 --> 00:20:29,408
That one.

571
00:20:29,408 --> 00:20:32,240
♪What I miss is wanting to love
even after the arguments♪

572
00:20:34,208 --> 00:20:35,136
(Instantly guessed out)
The Flower Guardian.

573
00:20:36,327 --> 00:20:37,216
(Sudden realization)

574
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:38,944
(No way)

575
00:20:39,120 --> 00:20:40,160
Bro, wait a moment.

576
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:42,680
(A master is here)
Come on, Lin Yi.

577
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,960
Let me think how Xingxu sang it.

578
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,128
(Recalling)

579
00:20:48,128 --> 00:20:51,264
♪ABCD ABCD♪

580
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:54,280
(Relieved)
There's still a way.

581
00:20:54,591 --> 00:20:55,712
(The insider's lips are tightly shut)

582
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,680
♪On the tropic♪

583
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,720
♪Of love, anticipating♪

584
00:20:58,720 --> 00:21:00,400
♪Meeting again. Sky will clear...♪

585
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,000
I got it.

586
00:21:02,152 --> 00:21:03,808
(Read successfully)

587
00:21:10,656 --> 00:21:17,248
(Everyone is off track)

588
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:18,920
♪Goodbye, my friend♪

589
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:19,270
Okay.

590
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:21,000
♪Goodbye, my friend♪

591
00:21:21,169 --> 00:21:23,456
(Friend, you've gone far away)

592
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:24,760
Is this the song?

593
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,048
(Self-doubt)

594
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:28,240
It's okay, let's go back a bit further.

595
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,880
From what I hear, this is it.

596
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:32,560
I think the problem should be with me.

597
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:33,640
(The onlooker is clear)
But I didn't let him know.

598
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,480
No, you sang it pretty well.

599
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,280
(The onlooker sees clearly)
Let him sing with headphones on.

600
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,600
I'll put on headphones.

601
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:39,680
Xingxu, sing with headphones on.

602
00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:42,320
♪If I could♪

603
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:45,640
♪I want to be with you,
back to the day we met♪

604
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,160
(Is this the song?)
♪Make time stop♪

605
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,560
♪Make time stop♪

606
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:49,680
Look, the two of them matched.

607
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,120
They matched.

608
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,200
The Flower Guardian.

609
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:54,656
Didn't I guess it right?

610
00:21:54,656 --> 00:21:56,288
(No!)

611
00:21:56,928 --> 00:21:58,336
(Of course)

612
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:01,640
Wen guessed it right.

613
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,600
The Flower Guardian.

614
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,616
I guessed it right.

615
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:04,680
I guessed it right.

616
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:05,840
(Vehemently complaining)
Lin Yi said it wasn't it

617
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:06,800
and told me to listen again.

618
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,360
I didn't recognize

619
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,440
(Innocent)
the song he was singing.

620
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,440
The Flower Guardian.

621
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,240
Didn't you recognize it?

622
00:22:11,520 --> 00:22:12,880
He didn't sing it in such

623
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:13,640
a tune.

624
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:17,480
It doesn't matter you didn't guess it.

625
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:19,720
But Yuwen guessed which song it was,

626
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,056
- and you said it was wrong.
- You said it was wrong.

627
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:24,160
- You said it wasn't it.
- I really wanted to cover your mouth.

628
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:27,968
When he sang it the first time,

629
00:22:27,968 --> 00:22:29,600
I already guessed the song.

630
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:30,784
Because the rhythm was exactly the same.

631
00:22:30,784 --> 00:22:31,200
Then he just...

632
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,880
"Listen again."

633
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,920
"It's wrong."

634
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,656
And he kept singing.

635
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:39,360
(Very suspicious)
You.

636
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:41,160
I...
